tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE shipping_carriers (
    carrier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    carrier_name STRING,
    location STRING,
    shipping_cost DECIMAL(10,2),
    delivery_time STRING
)

CREATE TABLE ShippingLabels (
    label_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    carrier_id INT,
    shipment_id INT,
    label_data BYTEA,
    FOREIGN KEY (carrier_id) REFERENCES ShippingCarriers(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (shipment_id) REFERENCES Shipments(shipment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE shipping_rates (
 rate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 carrier_id INT REFERENCES shipping_carriers(carrier_id),
 weight_min DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
 weight_max DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
 rate DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE shipping_rates (
  rate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  carrier_id INT,
  rate DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  weight_lb DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  CONSTRAINT fk_shipping_rates_carrier_id FOREIGN KEY (carrier_id) REFERENCES shipping_carriers(carrier_id)
);

CREATE TABLE shipments (
  shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  label_id INT,
  carrier_id INT,
  shipping_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  tracking_number VARCHAR(20) UNIQUE,
  CONSTRAINT fk_shipments_label_id FOREIGN KEY (label_id) REFERENCES shipping_labels(label_id),
  CONSTRAINT fk_shipments_carrier_id FOREIGN KEY (carrier_id) REFERENCES shipping_carriers(carrier_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ShippingPackages (
  package_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  package_weight DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  package_dimensions TEXT NOT NULL,
  location_id INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (location_id) REFERENCES ShippingLocations(location_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ShippingLabels (
  label_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  package_id INT NOT NULL,
  shipping_date DATE NOT NULL,
  shipping_cost DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  rate_id INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (package_id) REFERENCES ShippingPackages(package_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (rate_id) REFERENCES ShippingRates(rate_id)
);
